.ytimg.com/vi/sRTrcA3iS3k/hqdefault.jpg", "height": 360, "width": 480, "preference": -7, "id": "34", "resolution": "480x360"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/sRTrcA3iS3k/hqdefault.webp", "preference": -6, "id": "35"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sRTrcA3iS3k/sddefault.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 640, "preference": -5, "id": "36", "resolution": "640x480"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/sRTrcA3iS3k/sddefault.webp", "preference": -4, "id": "37"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sRTrcA3iS3k/hq720.jpg", "preference": -3, "id": "38"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/sRTrcA3iS3k/hq720.webp", "preference": -2, "id": "39"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sRTrcA3iS3k/maxresdefault.jpg", "preference": -1, "id": "40"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/sRTrcA3iS3k/maxresdefault.webp", "preference": 0, "id": "41"}], "thumbnail": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sRTrcA3iS3k/sddefault.jpg", "description": "PM Modi addressed an International Conference on Yoga organised by the Ministry of Ayush at Vigyan Bhavan in New Delhi.\n\nHere are the highlights from his speech:\n \nToday we are celebrating the first International Day of Yoga.\nAs I stand here today, the International Day of Yoga is being celebrated across the world, millions of people are participating in this event.\nIn India, this morning millions of people participated in a simple yoga demonstration at Rajpath (New Delhi), state and district capitals.\nThis coming together with our brother and sisters from other countries brings our hearts closer.\nYoga jeevan ko jee bharke jeeney ki jadi booti hai. (Yoga is the medicine to live life to the fullest)\nThe reach and spread of yoga spans continents and cuts across differences of colour, castes and creeds.\nThe body is a vehicle for the realisation of the Supreme Being.\nThe Gita says, Yoga is excellence at work.\nYoga is not an institution, it is a matter of faith.\nIf the body is a temple of the mind, Yoga creates a beautiful temple.\nThere is ample evidence that yoga helps in combating stress and chronic conditions.\nA Yogi is a person who is in harmony with himself, his body, surroundings and nature.\nPractice of Yoga leads to reduction of greed, coarseness and violence in an individual.\nIn a world of fear, Yoga creates courage and strength. A healthy body and disciplined mind is the foundation of a world without fear.\nYoga is not a sellable commodity. Yoga is for all humanity, we should not make it an exclusive preserve.", "channel_id": "UCEWHoHLo89dkQJR_axIupEA", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEWHoHLo89dkQJR_axIupEA", "duration": 2113, "view_count": 298, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sRTrcA3iS3k", "categories": ["News & Politics"], "tags": ["news", "express", "New Delhi (Indian City)", "Vigyan Bhavan (Location)", "Politics (TV Genre)", "India (Country)", "PM Modi", "PM Modi Yoga Day", "YogaDay", "International Day of Yoga", "International Yoga Day", "Yoga Day", "Yoga Day 2015", "baba ramdev", "yoga", "yoga for daily life", "healthy life style", "narendra modi", "pm modi", "modi sarkar", "world yoga day", "international yoga day", "21st june", "meditation", "peacefull life", "yoga the spiritual power", "power of soul", "yoga teacher", "cure", "cure of diseases"], "playable_in_embed": true, "live_status": "not_live", "media_type": "video", "_format_sort_fields": ["quality", "res", "fps", "hdr:12", "source", "vcodec", "channels", "acodec", "lang", "proto"], "automatic_captions": {"hi-orig": [{"ext": "json3", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/timedtext?v=sRTrcA3iS3k&ei=Ln0dav2wBs-rpt8P26S-6QY&caps=asr&opi=112496729&xoaf=5&xowf=1&hl=en&ip=0.0.0.0&ipbits=0&expire=1780342686&sparams=ip%2Cipbits%2Cexpire%2Cv%2Cei%2Ccaps%2Copi%2Cxoaf&signature=22B23182B13D480967DBE2204DDDFB314BCE8791.0752421F26AA9E88F5970ADA7690B5E894645D6B&key=yt8&kind=asr&lang=hi&fmt=json3", "name": "Hindi (Original)", "impersonate": true}, {"ext": "srv1", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/timed